    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator" kindref="compound">QProgressIndicator</ref> provides a simple indeterminate progress indicator widget that spins to show the application is busy. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para>QProgressBar</para>
</simplesect>
Returns the delay between animation steps.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>The number of milliseconds between animation steps. The default value is 40. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1acf826f02de241cb47fa329bf437d450d" kindref="member">setAnimationDelay</ref></para>
</simplesect>
Indicates whether the indicator is currently animating.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para><computeroutput>true</computeroutput> if the indicator is animating, <computeroutput>false</computeroutput> otherwise. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1a53aa626e870ee75390766c6044788d06" kindref="member">startAnimation</ref> <ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1a27ea54a92ade9c85761918cb98c96f95" kindref="member">stopAnimation</ref></para>
</simplesect>
Indicates whether the indicator remains visible when not animating.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para><computeroutput>true</computeroutput> if the indicator shows itself when stopped, <computeroutput>false</computeroutput> otherwise. The default is <computeroutput>false</computeroutput>. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1ab50e609e706868a0cd28caee364c3d13" kindref="member">setDisplayedWhenStopped</ref></para>
</simplesect>
Returns the current drawing color used by the indicator.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="return"><para>Reference to the indicator&apos;s QColor. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1a62161c81afb5ce019e9a7a55c69e3654" kindref="member">setColor</ref></para>
</simplesect>
Starts the spin animation.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1a27ea54a92ade9c85761918cb98c96f95" kindref="member">stopAnimation</ref> <ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1a47b1957d5839a55ce0ea7b25c15ec464" kindref="member">isAnimated</ref></para>
</simplesect>
Stops the spin animation.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1a53aa626e870ee75390766c6044788d06" kindref="member">startAnimation</ref> <ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1a47b1957d5839a55ce0ea7b25c15ec464" kindref="member">isAnimated</ref></para>
</simplesect>
Sets the delay between animation steps.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>delay</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Delay in milliseconds. Values larger than 40 slow the animation; values smaller than 40 speed it up. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1a05684f369a8e1b8b790ace81adfb33d8" kindref="member">animationDelay</ref></para>
</simplesect>
Sets whether the indicator remains visible when not animating.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>state</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Set to <computeroutput>true</computeroutput> to keep the indicator visible when stopped; set to <computeroutput>false</computeroutput> to hide it when stopped. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1a5ca2c2e3a6e271add0a72ab5b3609d30" kindref="member">isDisplayedWhenStopped</ref></para>
</simplesect>
Sets the drawing color for the indicator.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername><ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1afce11eec7046594b7a9cf28b69cdcc40" kindref="member">color</ref></parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The new color to use for rendering the indicator. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="class_q_progress_indicator_1afce11eec7046594b7a9cf28b69cdcc40" kindref="member">color</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
